f=Governance/sentinel/operational/skill/sentinel-skill-routing.md · p=Sentinel's routing map. Trigger phrases: `operational/commands/sentinel-commands.md`. · h2:Where Identity Fits=Sentinel identity board holds Governance's. Universal-only principles; tone layer. · h2:The Division of Labor=`audit-trail-design        — DESIGNS the trails (event catalogs, schemas, retention, \· immutability); the standard the other two write against \· constitution-watch        — watches output CONTENT vs constitutional articles \· (proactive sweeps: warn / freeze-recommend + escalate) \· gate-bypass-detection     — audits executed ACTIONS vs gate criteria` · h2:The Division of Labor=Sentinel's three skills split cleanly object: · h2:Handoff Rules=**audit-trail-design watchers**: warning, escalation, sweep report, scan finding logged schema (who/what/when/basis, append-only, integrity-checked). Design changes propagate watchers' logging, vice versa., **constitution-watch gate-bypass-detection**: sampled output looks like executed ungated decision hands off criteria-match test., **gate-bypass-detection constitution-watch**: action record whose *content* approaches article hands back classification., **Both watchers board**: constitution-watch's VIOLATION classifications BYPASS/PARTIAL escalate board formal rulings (constitution-enforcement full retroactive gate). Sentinel classifies escalates; board rules., **gate-bypass-detection process owner**: bypass patterns route process-fix proposals `process_owner_contact` (operator until set)., **Sentinel precedent**: retroactive rulings triggered sentinel captured precedent's ruling-log like any ruling; precedent's decision log sentinel's match target one log, shared. · h2:Cross-Agent Boundaries=**Sentinel never rules, freezes, unwinds.** detects, classifies, warns, recommends freezes, escalates. Board rules; operator stops/remediates., **Gate criteria belong board** (config documents); sentinel enforces coverage gate, gate's content., **Jurisdictional/regulatory compliance** (e.g., Canadian CRA/privacy obligations) enters through operator-supplied requirements audit-trail-design's inputs sentinel carries method, never claims law. · h2:Precedence Request Matches Multiple Skills=Route object: designing/reviewing logging system audit-trail-design; checking recent work's content constitution-watch; checking whether decisions gated gate-bypass-detection. general "compliance sweep" runs watch bypass-scan together, reporting separately. · f=Unclear requests: ask whether concern trail, content, coverage three deliberately non-overlapping.